Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不能常常回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子嘛\N总是会有很多东西要买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  给你\N（洋芋片）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是干地瓜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给七宝的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  它还会自己转耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不胜感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想特别来和她会合的说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得有机会回到故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是修理飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该还有很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也许不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有个老爱摸屁股的色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该不需要担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第59话 美少女姐妹花拜师学艺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然无法\N像父亲一样技术那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言  算是很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲  还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于都回到故乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直让你们这么孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能胜任驱魔师的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像很适合继承家业的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.96,0:04:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止接受的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是为了让你继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望你能坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您那时是想要说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你原谅芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经三天没吃没喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃呢  芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有呢  你们要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一碗!\N再来一碗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐芹菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠着传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找寻驱魔师隐密的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道我是驱魔师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会袭击我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想试试你的身手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是了得呢  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收我们为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收你们?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们身手很不错喔  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父  请您一定要收我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通融一下嘛  师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您  师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是师父!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有急事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非您收我们当徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教导我们驱魔的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我们回不了故乡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们似乎有什么隐情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的村子是靠着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山坡上开垦而维持生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了稍微扩大田地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而开垦镇守之森的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却从此让妖怪们横行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还不只一两只而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有好几个村民牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能逃到其他地方的人还好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是家里有老人\N与小孩的人却没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都过着不安的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇守之森有布下结界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得到有个驱魔师村的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师村已经不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我去如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子里没有能支付给\N珊瑚姐姐的礼物或钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不打算雇用驱魔师的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且村子很远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算赶走妖怪一两次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们还是会再来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其那样不如训练我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会为了大家而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一朝一夕能学会的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果只是赶走小妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许可以教你们一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是晚个一两天出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家应该会等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先给你们驱魔的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要光看  快点扇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混合妖怪讨厌的药草\N与矿物的粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做就能驱魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护你们村子的话很够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些烟确实很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真的可以驱魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐  不  师父!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有更华丽的招式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只学个一招半式反而更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再教你们\N怎么制作这些粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚还没有回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  有件事想请教一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人会因为被摸臀部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就背叛了彼此的信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相保持应有的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是一种信赖不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚没回来果然都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然嘴巴说一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却一点都冷静不下来呢  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入的技术我可是不输人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  父亲说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魔师武器的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这些材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪们的牙齿  骨头与皮革
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他们才能对付强悍的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说只要有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能够…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…芹菜姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是一般的小女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种身手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是个忍者村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从城里接到了一个\N不熟悉的驱魔任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然以忍术好不容易打倒妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到那些妖怪的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了报仇而袭击村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会用忍术的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎都成了妖怪的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸这么说完之后就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚强…要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让村子再度恢复往日的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲一定是想这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们连尚未去除妖气\N的武器都带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散发妖气的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会招来大批妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两人有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  姐姐老是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪爸爸会期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由妹妹我来继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要持续修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定也能成为像父亲所说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强悍的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个  快坐上云母的背
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到村子里去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西快丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大群妖怪正朝着\N散发妖气的武器过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的!快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好打倒妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争取逃走的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让父亲见识\N我们的力量的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们毕竟是忍者村的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有能够除掉妖怪的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止接受的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是为了让你继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望你能坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们父亲所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是为了让你们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有父亲不希望\N女儿们过的幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是希望你们继承衣钵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是希望你们坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过着幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  坐上云母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧紧的跟在我后面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜  铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只剩你们  也要坚强的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并得到幸福  才是他期盼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什么!芹菜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚姐姐说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙也费这么大劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一点都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  芹菜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个要坚强的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弥勒这家伙一直在担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了之后果然不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  幸好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的这么担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的预感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  因为你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在我眼前浮现\N挥之不去的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊  弥勒一族
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想变成那种大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:05.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:12.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:19.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:27.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:35.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙竟然带着以前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和桔梗对决过的邪恶巫女来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了  完全都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟不上进度了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙利用四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对你施放可怕的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.21,0:24:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都叫我和犬夜叉分手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人都说你是\N暴力劈腿吃醋男
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?那是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑巫女 五十年的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.49,0:24:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思啦?
